WHAT THIS COVERS

The compilation and editorial work — the structuring of records, the links
between records, Government Orders, Acts and manifesto promises, the domain
categorisation, the evidence grades, and the generated reports in docs/.

WHAT THIS DOES NOT COVER

The underlying source documents themselves. Tamil Nadu Government Orders,
Gazette notifications, Acts, Bills, Assembly proceedings and the government's
published achievement volumes belong to their issuing authorities and carry
their own terms. This project claims no ownership of them and grants no rights
over them. Text quoted from those documents is reproduced for reference and
remains the property of the issuing authority.

The manifesto promise statuses are reproduced from an external tracker and
remain that tracker's assessment, not this project's.

