PLEASE CARRY THE CAVEATS

Attribution is a legal requirement; the following is a request. This dataset
records what the Tamil Nadu government reported about itself. No record in it
is independently verified: no record is graded above D (sanctioned), and 376 of
438 rest solely on government-published summaries. If you reuse the numbers,
please carry that qualification with them. Presenting this data as verified
fact would reproduce exactly the problem this project was rebuilt to fix.
